title: Ebro In the Morning - Kanye Vs. Billie Eillish + Ben Simmons to Brooklyn

itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 2/11/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio talking about the NBA trade deadline(23 & 43), Kanye Vs. Billie Eilish(10 + 27), and ride or die (16)!  

Get excited for Black Facts and the also the gurus help solve your problems. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
